==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Incompossible
<hw>In`com*pos"si*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>in-</ets> not + <ets>compossible</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>incompossible</ets>.]</ety> <def>Not capable of joint existence;
incompatible; inconsistent.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Ambition and faith . . . are . . . <qex>incompossible</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Jer. Taylor.</qau></rj></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>In`com*pos`si*bil"i*ty</wf> <pr>(#)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <mark>[Obs.]</mark></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Incomprehense</ent>⟦br⟧
